1. *Pogledam* li u ogledalo, nikad se nebi zaljubila u sebe. (If I look in the mirror, I would never fall in love with myself.) 
2. *Pogledala* sam u njegovo lice i shvatila da sam ludo zaljubljena. (I looked at his face and realized that I'm madly in love.)
3. *Pogleda* li se sada, shvatices da nije isto. (If you look at it now, you will realize it's not the same.) 
4. On je *pogledao* u moje oci i shvatio da sam tu≈æan. (He looked into my eyes and realized that I was sad.)
5. *Pogledaj* kako lepo izgleda ova slika. (Look how beautiful this picture looks.)